tournament.motion: THBT parents should teach their children that the world is fair
THBT the LGBTQ+ movement should emphasise family values as a part of their activism, rather than adopting the view that family values do not matter

THBT major polluters should offer climate asylum and eventual citizenship to the people of island nations affected by rising sea levels, rather than attempting to curb those rising sea levels and their effects(constructing coastal infrastructure, such as sea walls and drainage networks; preventative efforts, such as reducing carbon and greenhouse gas emissions; mitigation efforts, such as the relocation of villages and infrastructure to higher elevations; and the building of artificial islands)

THR the rise of family channels Family channels are YouTube channels or social media accounts where families-often those with young children-share their daily lives. These channels feature a wide range of content, including but not limited to parenting tips, fun family activities, and vlogs of the family's routine. Many family channels are monetized, receive brand deals, or sell their own merchandise. Examples include The Ace Family, The Anazala Family, and Family Fun Pack
THW impose a 'digital data' tax on tech companies proportionate to the amount of user data they collect and use

In countries where a revolution has overturned a previous system, THP technocratic governments to democratic governments A technocratic government is one where leaders are appointed from among the citizens of a country on the basis of their technical expertise in a particular field (finance, health, education)
TH, as the feminist movement, W enourage the narrative that "women are selfish"
THR society's emphasis on being positive and optimistic in the face of adversity
